UMSOLWA, othinteka ecaleni lokubulala umlisa owayephuma ukuyocima ukoma kamakhelwane wakhe, uzobuyela Nkantolo yeMantshi eVerulam,  ngoMeyi. UMnuz Wandile Gumede (19), ogcinwe ezitokisini,  kubikwa ukuthi walimaza  kanzima umufi, uMnuz Ayanda Ndlovu ( 28) waseMalentshisini, eMahlabathini, ngemuva kwengxabano okungaziwa ukuthi yasuswa yini ngesikhathi behlangana ezintathakusa,  ngoMashi 7. Umsolwa kubikwa ukuthi wavimba umufi, obefundisa eCottonlands, eVerulam,  wambuza ukuthi kungani ezitshela. Kuthiwa uMnuz Gumede wakhipha uhalakasha lommese abhokoda ngawo umufi kathathu esifubeni. Umufi wabizelwa abezimo eziphuthumayo kodwa wagcina ngokuphangalala endaweni yesigameko. Amalungu omphakathi, ayefuna ukutitinya umsolwa, kubikwa ukuthi anqandwa wukufika kwamaphoyisa adambisa isimo. La malungu ayesola ukuthi umsolwa wayedle izidakamizwa ngenkathi enza lesi senzo njengoba kuthiwa ubaziwa ukuthi ubezidayisa. Okhulumela amaphoyisa KwaZulu-Natal, uColonel Thembeka Mbele, usiqinisekisile isigameko sokugwazwa komlisa eVerulam. “Amaphoyisa avule icala lokubulala. Kulindeleke ukuthi umsolwa aphindele eNkantolo yeMantshi eVerulam ngoMeyi 18,” kubeka uCol Mbele. 